# Dockerfile (helper)
# This repository contains multiple services (Node.js and Python). Use the service-specific Dockerfiles provided:
# - Dockerfile.node      -> Node.js service (server/ or root)
# - Dockerfile.python    -> Python FastAPI service (inference-service/ or root)
#
# To build the Node image:
#   docker build -f Dockerfile.node -t digicloset-node:latest .
# To build the Python image:
#   docker build -f Dockerfile.python -t digicloset-python:latest .
#
# If you want a single Dockerfile for a chosen service, copy/rename the appropriate file to Dockerfile.